**Data Jobs Visualization Dashboard – Power BI**

**Project Overview**

This project presents an interactive Data Jobs  Dashboard built using Microsoft Power BI. The dashboard analyzes trends in the data job market around the globe, including job roles, salaries, required skills, and job distribution across locations.

The goal of this project is to transform raw job market data into meaningful insights that can help aspiring data professionals understand industry trends.

**Objectives**

Analyze demand for different data-related job roles

Identify top skills required in the data industry

Explore salary trends across job titles

Understand geographical distribution of data jobs

Provide insights for individuals pursuing a career in data analytics

**Tools & Technologies Used**

Microsoft Power BI

Power Query (Data Cleaning & Transformation)

DAX (Data Analysis Expressions)

Data Modeling

Interactive Data Visualization

**Dashboard Features**

Job role distribution analysis

Median Salary comparison across different data roles

Skills demand visualization

Geographic job distribution

Interactive filters and slicers

**Dashboard Preview**



